headline: The PLANTERS® Brand Celebrates National Nut Day with the Return of Special Reserve Peanuts
summary: Back by popular demand and available beginning today, Oct. 22, on National Nut Day, the PLANTERS® brand is reintroducing PLANTERS® Special Reserve peanuts. With their debut last holiday season, this limited-edition peanut is crafted for the refined palate of true peanut connoisseurs and arrives just in time for holiday gifting.
